Properties.Caption: Просмотр парных проводок
Properties.Tag: Select [EX_DT_CT].[EX_NUMID] As [Номер проводки], [EX_DT_CT].[DBN] As [Дата проводки], Rtrim([K_EX_OP].[CEX_OP]) As [Операция проводки], [EX_DT_CT].[NUM] As [Номер], Sgn([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 16) As [Баланс бюджета], Sgn([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 8) As [Баланс казначейства], Sgn([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 4) As [Баланс учреждения], [K_BS_DT].[CBS] As [Балансовый счет дебета], [K_BS_CT].[CBS] As [Балансовый счет кредита], [K_TD_DT].[CTD] As [Тип документа дебета], [K_TD_CT].[CTD] As [Тип документа кредита], Sum([EX_DT_CT].[SUMM]) As [Сумма] From ((((([EX_DT_CT] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_EX_OP] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_EX_OPID]=[K_EX_OP].[K_EX_OPID])) Left Join [K_BS] As [K_BS_DT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_BSID_DT]=[K_BS_DT].[K_BSID])) Left Join [K_BS] As [K_BS_CT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_BSID_CT]=[K_BS_CT].[K_BSID])) Left Join [K_TD] As [K_TD_DT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_TDID_DT]=[K_TD_DT].[K_TDID])) Left Join [K_TD] As [K_TD_CT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_TDID_CT]=[K_TD_CT].[K_TDID])) Where |0 Group by [EX_DT_CT].[EX_NUMID], [EX_DT_CT].[DBN], Rtrim([K_EX_OP].[CEX_OP]), [EX_DT_CT].[NUM], Sgn([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 16), Sgn([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 8), Sgn([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 4), [K_BS_DT].[CBS], [K_BS_CT].[CBS], [K_TD_DT].[CTD], [K_TD_CT].[CTD] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр парных проводок
